            "description": "As an architect I worked together with the team of EWB-NL, Young Urban Achievers and Spark on a design for Kriterion Monrovia, the first art-house cinema in Liberia. The students envisioned a cinema which could also serve as a cultural hub, with space for art, music, debate and social gathering in their capital city. We provided them with a concept design that enable them to see this dreaming coming true and become materialized. Taking in account the local building techniques, cultural expressions and the context brought us exciting challenge. We poured all this inspiration into an elemental, minimalistic and at the same time expressive building design that is ready for the future. \n\nAlso see: https://www.ewbnl.org/ewb-netherlands-liberia-art-house-theater/"
